{"tid":1839741,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己可有可無 一啲都唔獨特","createTime":"2020-01-24T14:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T15:24:52.000Z","uid":205742,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"89781cd31cf637ce753b41f96fd9aa9c634719cc","tid":1839741,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"好想俾人愛 但係又會覺得自己唔夠愛佢好內疚 對住真係鍾意嘅人只係想show最真實嘅自己比人睇 可惜呢個自己一啲都唔型 無人欣賞 無人要<br />\n<br />\n正常朋友對我嘅評價同我自我評價亦都係180度嘅唔同 究竟我係太假定係我根本唔認識我自己 <br />\n我係咪要做一啲自己唔想或者自己好厭惡嘅行為先至會俾人鍾意俾人錫，但到頭來我想要嘅嘢係會將我一直建立緊嘅畫皮撕破，究竟我係邊個 <br />\n<br />\n點解唔可以有個我都鍾意嘅人無保留咁愛我 可以包容我 唔覺得我kam 唔覺得我同其他人唔同係怪<br />\n<br />\n我好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e01e36c72db22680777ff74b0c9f589ca0f0630","tid":1839741,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"又叫春<br />\n好似屋企隻貓久唔久就不停喵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135003f0dc69ee3e83c6d19d981d4cfd6eeef2d4","tid":1839741,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e01e36c72db22680777ff74b0c9f589ca0f0630","tid":1839741,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"又叫春<br />\n好似屋企隻貓久唔久就不停喵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"唔俾呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f78a48d321bb136de6690d4af2093d4568384f37","tid":1839741,"uid":227645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce137457c32102530534b907e59cecda978cbd9e","tid":1839741,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f78a48d321bb136de6690d4af2093d4568384f37","tid":1839741,"uid":227645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:39:48.000Z","msg"